      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "WATCH HER WIN (3) was a last-start winner from the rails at Taree Super Track over 300m (17.58) after charging straight to the lead, scoring by a neck. Can continue winning ways. AT THE GATE (7) boasts a strong record this journey with six wins and five minors from 16 tries. Comes off a (17.47) win last time, scoring by 2.5 lengths in a Grade 5 over 300m at Taree Super Track. Among the main chances. MARRA LAD (1) unwanted in betting but showed good early dash and led until late, finishing second and beaten 0.8 lengths (17.82) at Taree Super Track in a Grade 5 over 300m. Reliable out of the boxes and should take advantage of the inside draw. Will give a great sight again. RAINING BOURBON (8) has hardly put a foot wrong of late and will be competitive again.",
